::Firearm::

Firearm nods. "Welcome to the Maximals then!" he says entusiastically, 
looking at the two new Maximals, "Do you need a CR or anything?"

He turns around, setting off toward the Cybertronian Fire and motioning for 
the two new bots to follow.
